You just got a glimpse of what I do behind the camera.

01:08:25.310 --> 01:08:28.662
I am who I am, and I believe what I believe.

01:08:28.662 --> 01:08:30.845
I'm not ashamed of it.

01:08:30.845 --> 01:08:45.684
I try to maintain a positive filter, but I'm telling you, we're entering into a storm and most of you are blind to it.

01:08:49.937 --> 01:08:50.069
The body of Christ has its head in the sand.

01:08:50.069 --> 01:08:52.640
Wake up, church!

01:08:52.640 --> 01:08:53.479
Wake up!

01:08:53.479 --> 01:09:00.907
You're running out of time.

01:09:23.703 --> 01:09:24.835
This last year went by like vapor.

01:09:43.194 --> 01:09:43.451
I drink my juice at night—I love my organic grapefruit juice; Diana buys it for me, no sugar added.

01:09:43.451 --> 01:09:45.110
Father, we worship You.

01:09:45.110 --> 01:09:48.600
We glorify Your name in all the earth.

01:09:48.600 --> 01:09:56.109
We magnify Your name.

01:09:56.109 --> 01:09:57.320
Thank You, Father.

01:09:57.320 --> 01:10:26.100
We call in the blessing right now in Jesus' name from the north, the south, the east, and the west—that there's breakthrough in 2026 to get the job done.

01:10:26.100 --> 01:11:00.778
Thank You, Lord.

01:11:00.778 --> 01:11:02.271
Okay, I'm in Venezuela.

01:11:24.684 --> 01:11:25.546
I see our troops again.

01:11:25.546 --> 01:11:28.280
Have we gone in there?

01:11:28.280 --> 01:11:37.587
That's interesting; I don't think there's anything about that.

01:11:41.280 --> 01:11:42.450
I see our troops on the ground there, protecting the oil wells.

01:11:51.360 --> 01:11:51.680
I see the Marines and the big domes.

01:11:51.680 --> 01:12:14.997
Those big barrels—I see our people around those big white barrels, thousands of gallons, storage places.

01:12:14.997 --> 01:12:25.640
I see little drones flying around in the sky, surveilling.

01:12:25.640 --> 01:12:30.920
We pray over our troops and our people.

01:12:30.920 --> 01:12:41.070
Lord, why are You showing me this tonight?

01:13:12.462 --> 01:13:12.644
I pray for our people.

01:13:12.644 --> 01:13:13.920
Oh, I see it now.

01:13:36.350 --> 01:13:36.660
I see men with AKs coming out of the woods—drug lords trying to ambush.

01:13:36.660 --> 01:13:40.800
They're coming out of what looks like a tropical forest.

01:13:40.800 --> 01:13:43.040
These are guerrillas.

01:13:49.840 --> 01:13:50.140
I hear guerrilla warfare is coming.

01:13:50.140 --> 01:14:06.985
Drug lords are trying to overflow people with their money; these are street civilians who have been paid to join up with drug lords.

01:14:06.985 --> 01:14:16.432
They're being paid big money.

01:14:16.432 --> 01:14:18.568
You need to hear.

01:14:18.568 --> 01:14:22.382
Listen to me, President.

01:14:22.382 --> 01:14:33.193
They're being paid big money.

01:14:37.835 --> 01:14:44.551
I see young men 17, 18, 19 years old being paid by drug lords.

01:14:48.824 --> 01:14:59.264
Some of them are being held by their families, being told, 'You do this for us or we're going to wipe your grandma out.

01:14:59.264 --> 01:15:22.280
' I see young men with white t-shirts and black hair coming up out of the woods to try to ambush our people like soldiers.

01:15:22.280 --> 01:15:26.795
Our people are trained fighters; these people are not.

01:15:32.488 --> 01:15:37.234
I see cocktails with alcohol and fire in them; I see Molotov cocktails today.

01:15:37.234 --> 01:15:44.850
They still want to take out the oil wells to damage the economy in retaliation.

01:15:44.850 --> 01:16:04.790
I'm seeing Russian troops coming into Venezuela.

01:16:04.800 --> 01:16:09.811
How is that possible, Father, with how stretched they are in Ukraine?

01:16:09.811 --> 01:16:12.320
There are not very many.

01:16:12.320 --> 01:16:17.620
They say they're trying to keep peace.

01:16:17.620 --> 01:16:26.880
They want to come in and be another party to keep peace for their interests.

01:16:26.880 --> 01:16:28.464
They have interests.

01:16:28.464 --> 01:16:33.743
They look like our soldiers.

01:17:17.000 --> 01:17:17.223
They're coming up from Brazil, coming over by Brazil, up here in this corner, and they're coming down like this.

01:17:17.223 --> 01:17:21.691
I see them up by Brazil.

01:17:21.691 --> 01:17:25.720
Yeah, they're going to come through Brazil.

01:17:27.526 --> 01:17:47.760
A turf war, but it will be involving Russia in the days ahead—a turf war involving Russia concerning Venezuela and Cuba.

01:18:04.888 --> 01:18:11.234
Cuba is what I've seen, Braden, and now Cuba is involved with this.

01:18:22.480 --> 01:18:23.440
They're trying to devise a plan.

01:18:23.440 --> 01:18:46.234
I see our people on the ground going in and getting these drug lords out.

01:18:48.264 --> 01:18:49.080
Their boots are on the ground.

01:18:56.983 --> 01:18:57.440
Our people are on the ground right now taking out key targets.

01:18:59.840 --> 01:19:00.514
It's like an invasion.

01:19:13.335 --> 01:19:15.049
I see coke everywhere.

01:19:31.340 --> 01:19:31.690
I see coke plants being blown up.

01:19:31.690 --> 01:19:40.810
I see fire, I see smoke, I see coke powder burning.

01:19:40.810 --> 01:19:57.680
Our Marines, our people are going through and I see them taking them out—a ground invasion.

01:20:08.655 --> 01:20:26.707
People who are highly trained, like Navy Seals, are taking these people and trying to get rid of these labs.

01:20:26.707 --> 01:20:33.480
But I see Russia coming from the east.

01:20:33.480 --> 01:20:41.160
I see there's probably 10,000 of them coming through Brazil into Venezuela.

01:20:41.160 --> 01:20:49.504
They want to be peacemakers, like, 'We're coming to regulate.

01:20:49.504 --> 01:21:04.060
' Even though I speak English, the words are like peacemakers, like a peace treaty, ensuring they have a say, not just America.

01:21:05.260 --> 01:21:07.360
It's about the oil.

01:21:07.360 --> 01:21:11.840
But Cuba will go along with Russia.

01:21:11.840 --> 01:21:15.800
Those aren't all Russian soldiers; they're Cuban.

01:21:27.787 --> 01:21:28.433
These are just a couple of combat-trained men, but Cuba knows the territory.

01:21:28.433 --> 01:21:46.769
They've been there a long time, and they're using these Cuban men because they know the territory.

01:21:48.446 --> 01:21:53.120
They're going into Brazil and coming from Brazil—that's a very clear, dominant vision.

01:22:11.940 --> 01:22:12.265
I need to let you know that this is a very colorful, dominant vision.

01:22:39.320 --> 01:22:53.448
It's jungle—lots of jungle.

01:22:53.448 --> 01:23:41.220
I see greens, trees, and vines.

01:23:41.220 --> 01:24:09.920
So, with them coming that direction, what does that do?

01:25:23.617 --> 01:25:24.154
It just raises tension because I see the drug wars and these young men with white t-shirts and blue jeans.

01:25:36.120 --> 01:25:37.848
They're being paid to try to get people away from the oil.

01:25:57.950 --> 01:25:58.340
They want to take out the oil refineries.

01:25:58.340 --> 01:26:02.560
They don't want America getting that money.

01:26:02.560 --> 01:26:10.707
If that's what they're there for, it will eliminate them wanting to be here.

01:26:10.707 --> 01:26:13.330
It costs them more money to start it up.

01:26:13.330 --> 01:26:23.240
They're upset because it's about the drugs and their livelihood.

01:26:23.240 --> 01:26:31.110
It's about big money and drugs.

01:26:31.120 --> 01:26:38.813
But it's not just about America's drugs; this is Europe's drugs.

01:26:38.813 --> 01:26:44.995
It's like a cocaine highway—a trafficking highway that goes throughout Europe and America.

01:26:51.880 --> 01:26:52.040
I see it going into Canada and parts of Asia.

01:26:52.200 --> 01:26:53.315
This is a cocaine highway.

01:26:53.315 --> 01:27:15.630
Even parts of Africa are affected by this.

01:27:15.640 --> 01:27:17.594
Africa is highlighted very much.

01:27:17.594 --> 01:27:20.813
South Africa spreads like veins.

01:27:20.813 --> 01:27:38.584
They take these drugs and bring them in.

01:27:38.584 --> 01:28:00.813
There's interest of drug money everywhere.

01:28:00.813 --> 01:28:09.990
It's like a clashing of the two fronts together concerning Russia, America, and Cuba.

01:28:14.600 --> 01:28:16.760
This is mainly Cuba.

01:28:16.760 --> 01:28:22.672
Cuba is asking Russia for help.

01:28:22.672 --> 01:28:38.560
Remember the alliance I told you about.

01:28:38.560 --> 01:28:43.091
I see a lot of Cuban men.

01:28:43.091 --> 01:28:43.937
Amen.

01:29:20.280 --> 01:29:20.535
We pray over all of it.

01:29:20.535 --> 01:29:22.316
We just thank you, Lord.

01:29:22.316 --> 01:29:24.120
There's a de-escalation of everything.

01:29:26.060 --> 01:29:28.351
I don't know, Lord, what this is all about, but I've seen it really clear.

01:29:29.529 --> 01:29:32.256
I thank you, Lord, for your hand.

01:29:33.760 --> 01:29:34.491
I see Claudia.

01:29:34.491 --> 01:29:36.543
Great pressure on Claudia.

01:29:36.543 --> 01:29:38.500
She's in a lot of fear.

01:29:38.500 --> 01:29:40.360
She thinks she's next.

01:29:40.360 --> 01:29:41.063
She's pacing.

01:29:41.063 --> 01:29:52.216
Claudia is in an office and she's pacing.

01:29:52.216 --> 01:29:53.880
She's very upset.

01:29:53.880 --> 01:29:59.275
She's not sleeping at night, thinking she's next.

01:29:59.275 --> 01:30:04.128
It's a level of paranoia on Claudia.

01:30:04.128 --> 01:30:11.280
But the man over Cuba is down under the ground.

01:30:11.280 --> 01:30:23.820
I see him in the side of a cliff.

01:30:23.820 --> 01:30:29.954
The man in Cuba has a light on in the ground and I'm seeing him.

01:30:29.954 --> 01:30:33.600
He has a blue shirt on.

01:30:33.600 --> 01:30:47.773
He's under the ground and he has soldiers all around him.

01:31:03.680 --> 01:31:04.340
It looks like the side of a hill.

01:31:04.340 --> 01:31:09.010
He's inside of a mountain.

01:31:09.010 --> 01:31:21.280
He has a bunker in the side of a mountain.

01:31:21.280 --> 01:31:28.956
If you look at the island, it's on the side facing America.

01:31:28.956 --> 01:31:30.884
I can see this bunker.

01:31:30.884 --> 01:31:31.893
It's very luxurious.

01:31:31.893 --> 01:31:35.504
He's hiding down there on high alert.

01:31:35.504 --> 01:31:43.512
I see soldiers all around him with Cuban colors on.

01:31:43.512 --> 01:31:48.695
I see red hats—some look like a beret.

01:31:48.695 --> 01:31:49.460
He's African.

01:31:49.460 --> 01:31:51.337
This man is very stocky.

01:31:52.740 --> 01:31:54.040
There's a secret passage to this place.

01:32:05.840 --> 01:32:06.120
I see palm trees and greenery, but it's down a trail.

01:32:06.120 --> 01:32:09.920
There are communications—TV antennas coming off of here.

01:32:09.920 --> 01:32:15.952
Claudia's in a house with antique cherrywood furniture around her.

01:32:27.058 --> 01:32:27.236
I see a carved wood chair and an old post bed.

01:32:27.769 --> 01:32:29.640
It looks like an old plantation house with dark wood.

01:32:29.640 --> 01:32:30.257
Beautiful furniture.

01:32:30.257 --> 01:32:33.000
They're talking back and forth on the phone.

01:32:33.000 --> 01:32:38.183
She's really concerned.

01:32:38.183 --> 01:32:44.041
He is at ease.

01:32:44.041 --> 01:32:47.525
He's in the ground.

01:32:47.525 --> 01:32:48.140
She's pacing.

01:32:48.140 --> 01:32:48.755
She's worried.

01:32:48.755 --> 01:33:07.604
He's talking to her like he doesn't care, acting arrogant.

01:33:07.604 --> 01:33:14.995
He has all kinds of missiles and armory around him.

01:33:14.995 --> 01:33:27.407
Does Cuba have a military like that?

01:33:27.407 --> 01:33:36.067
Now, it may sound really dumb, y'all.

01:33:59.591 --> 01:33:59.800
I'm sorry, but I'm seeing a military around this guy.

01:33:59.800 --> 01:34:00.858
They have their own military.

01:34:00.858 --> 01:34:09.630
They have their own stuff.

01:34:09.640 --> 01:34:19.310
Well, of course, they're a country.

01:34:19.320 --> 01:34:26.200
It's not like America, of course, but they have red berets on their heads.

01:34:28.080 --> 01:35:12.780
And he's communicating to him that they want to take their people and their military to go over and through Brazil, come over onto Venezuela and cause jungle warfare against our troops.

01:35:27.166 --> 01:35:27.389
You hear me?

01:35:27.389 --> 01:35:28.280
It's very clear.

01:35:28.280 --> 01:35:31.350
It's a very detailed vision.

01:35:43.291 --> 01:35:43.497
They want to send their people through the backway.

01:35:55.968 --> 01:35:56.112
And I see drug lords on the other side; they're coming from Colombia.

01:35:56.112 --> 01:35:59.140
It's on two fronts: Colombia and Brazil.

01:36:01.700 --> 01:36:08.360
And I see them trying to trickle in because they want the oil.

01:36:08.360 --> 01:36:13.440
He's trying to be real radical.

01:36:28.030 --> 01:36:28.380
He has nothing to lose—everything to lose, his life—but in his mind, he doesn't care about those people.

01:36:28.380 --> 01:36:29.780
Thank you, Lord.

01:36:29.780 --> 01:36:41.770
It's Colombia, and it's about the trafficking of drugs, protecting their assets of drugs, the coke, the refineries.

01:36:41.770 --> 01:36:51.535
There are some major, humongous plants inside.

01:36:51.535 --> 01:37:01.365
You see metal buildings that the metal is like a wavy metal—tin that is wavy tin, indented like a wave.

01:37:16.880 --> 01:37:17.034
And on the side of these buildings, it's rusted.

01:37:17.034 --> 01:37:23.070
And there's coke being made in these buildings down by Colombia.

01:37:23.080 --> 01:37:24.700
It's on the border.

01:37:24.700 --> 01:37:32.133
And I see these big factories.

01:37:32.133 --> 01:37:40.436
Outside, there are workers that are like slave workers making coke.

01:37:40.436 --> 01:37:46.010
It's down by Venezuela, Cuba, and Colombia.

01:37:46.010 --> 01:37:49.291
Thank you, Holy Ghost.

01:37:49.291 --> 01:37:53.352
And this is what Cuba is involved in.

01:37:53.352 --> 01:37:59.693
They're trying to go and protect some of these assets.

01:37:59.693 --> 01:38:06.095
These are major drug plants.

01:38:06.095 --> 01:38:09.270
Huge.

01:38:20.080 --> 01:38:24.670
, the drug lords are scrambling to try to pay for this because they know America's coming.

01:38:34.890 --> 01:38:35.325
Do you understand what I'm saying to you, son?

01:38:35.325 --> 01:38:37.200
I see Colombia very clear.

01:38:42.719 --> 01:38:43.199
And I see drugs.

01:38:43.199 --> 01:38:49.120
And these drug lords are paying Cuba to come and help protect their assets with guerrilla warfare, AK-47s, things like that.

01:38:49.120 --> 01:38:51.160
These men are trained.

01:38:51.160 --> 01:38:53.067
This is big money.

01:38:53.067 --> 01:38:55.051
It's about the pesos.

01:38:55.051 --> 01:38:58.960
It's about the dinero with the pesos.

01:38:58.960 --> 01:39:06.910
It's all connected—the triangle—but the trafficking of the drugs comes up through the southern border underneath those tunnels, and it's all connected.

01:39:12.502 --> 01:39:12.680
And it comes out the Panama Canal.

01:39:12.680 --> 01:39:14.060
I see Panama highlighted.

01:39:24.840 --> 01:39:25.233
And they use this to smuggle the drugs into Asia.

01:39:25.233 --> 01:39:27.893
This is big money, Braden.

01:39:34.010 --> 01:39:34.255
I'm talking billions of dollars.

01:39:35.615 --> 01:39:37.920
And they're scrambling around like rats because they know he's coming.

01:39:51.942 --> 01:39:52.178
But it's our military.

01:39:53.480 --> 01:40:04.200
But they're bringing in their military, and they're going to try to set up booby traps against our people to stop the drug trafficking and the sex trafficking because there's so much money involved in this.

01:40:04.200 --> 01:40:07.823
Claudia is pacing, and I see that other guy.

01:40:07.823 --> 01:40:09.720
He's hiding in a bunker.

01:40:09.720 --> 01:40:12.180
He's in a mountain.

01:40:12.180 --> 01:40:16.103
Now, if I'm missing it, it could be a metaphor.

01:40:33.864 --> 01:40:34.288
I don't even know if Cuba has a mountain.

01:40:34.288 --> 01:40:40.991
So, I'm just telling you, if they don't have a mountain, don't sit there and throw stones at me.

01:40:40.991 --> 01:40:51.815
I'm trying to tell you, I see this man in the side of a mountain.

01:41:10.343 --> 01:41:11.647
So, I'm just telling you what I see.

01:41:11.647 --> 01:41:16.155
Okay?

01:41:34.220 --> 01:41:34.480
It's also in the jungle around him.

01:41:42.560 --> 01:41:42.729
I see him down in there.

01:41:42.729 --> 01:41:45.378
It's a nice bunker, a luxury bunker.

01:41:45.378 --> 01:41:47.705
How long, son, have I been doing this?

01:41:47.705 --> 01:41:48.485
This isn't over.

01:41:48.485 --> 01:41:51.110
This is not anywhere near over.

01:41:51.110 --> 01:41:56.903
We're about to see some stuff we didn't want to see.

01:41:56.903 --> 01:42:08.510
But young people will be involved in this.

01:42:08.520 --> 01:42:13.040
They're going to retaliate for what happened to Maduro.

01:42:13.040 --> 01:42:18.380
I see them trying to rise up and cause turmoil.

01:42:18.380 --> 01:42:21.960
It's more about Colombia highlighted even more than it is Venezuela.

01:42:21.960 --> 01:42:25.200
This is very serious about Colombia, but it's big money and big drugs.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
But Cuba has an interest in it, and so does Claudia.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
A lot of corruption here.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Very serious, all that I'm seeing.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
We need a major army if we're going to do all this.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
I mean, seriously, we need to protect our people.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
But on this, I see drones flying around—our drones.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.750
I see our military, and they're all stationed, and they're going to put a big base in Venezuela in the days ahead on the water.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
It's a major port on the northern side.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
They'll put a base on the northern side of Venezuela up toward the water.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
There's a port there, and it'll be a place of a major military base on the water.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Lord, we're so grateful for all that you show us here.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
We're so thankful for all that you show us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
We couldn't do this without you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Of course, Lord, it's almost one.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
I think we're done.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
There's something very wrong.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
This is very serious concerning America and Cuba.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Cuba is very aggressive because they have Russia backing them.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
And I see Russian troops in this.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
I'm trying to tell you, we have to pray for Florida.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
We pray for Florida.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
We pray over Miami.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
We pray over the Keys.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
We pray over the cruise ships.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:12.600
We thank you, Lord, that there's a hedge of protection around the cruise ships and the cruise ship industry and all of our boats, all of our oil tankers, all of our people, our freight boats.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
Father, I pray a hedge of protection over our military, over our assets, our cruise ships, all of it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:12.950
Now, it's hard for me to tell seasons because it's down by the water, and I don't know what it looks like down there in the middle of their seasons, but this season looks like it's pretty.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
I'm trying to look at the sun and where it's at in the sky.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
That looks like a summer sun to me, but that's down by the equator.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
All I can say is we're in a time like I've never seen before.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
I have such caution for America right now.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
I pray over Hawaii.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.050
I pray over Honolulu and our military bases in Hawaii and the families, and I thank you, Lord, that every island is covered.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
No Pearl Harbor experiences.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
I don't know when this will be, so I'm not even going to say that concerning China.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.800
I pray over our military bases in Hawaii and all the islands, and I thank you, Father, that they're always in the right place at the right time.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
And Father, I thank you, Lord, that your hedge is around and about Hawaii.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
So thank you, Lord, for all the people in Africa, Australia, New Zealand, the Philippines, South Korea, all of them.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Father, I pray over every single person who's represented here tonight.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
We pray for a supernatural revival in their nations in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
We call a stirring in North Korea tonight.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
We thank you, Lord, that Kim Jong-un's days are over.

